{"tid":621641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華明邨毒狗】大埔CID再陪 勁索勁靚女狗主 返現場調查","createTime":"2018-04-08T13:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T14:12:37.000Z","uid":53705,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f40262af285649ba37b4c13c1bc535038f17cfcd","tid":621641,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:17:22.000Z","msg":"粉嶺華明邨發生連環毒狗案，至少4隻居民所養犬隻死亡。警方高度重視案件，交大埔警區刑事偵緝隊第五隊跟進調查，多名探員今早9時許陪同兩名狗主，當中包括9歲半松鼠狗「安力史」的狗主余小姐，再在華明邨內協助調查蒐證，並沿著平日放狗路線步行。其間在禮明樓對開花槽發現被放置的食物，但未有撿走化驗，眾人在邨內逗留約一小時後離開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180407/large/1523069835_8636.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180407%2Flarge%2F1523069835_8636.jpg&h=55b5c14b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個狗主好靚女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f6b40e669335d7aed309d02b9d198a498d5bd8","tid":621641,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3065e7839b6df0881363439633ab69e6bee615ca","tid":621641,"uid":53705,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"靚女狗主: 警方高度重視案件<br />\n毒撚狗主: 警方:「屌, 阻住我收工, 快快手 close file」"},{"pid":"940b239ea7dc9fae016c64533e7b03232330f3ac","tid":621641,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83add915017669a46a5621c94578abb5e4ef78cb","tid":621641,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:30:03.000Z","msg":"正<br />\n又有眼耳口鼻又盛"},{"pid":"f239f840ac327747a232a0c7df660e68c62dd82d","tid":621641,"uid":51134,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:33:42.000Z","msg":"一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_m7rz4xNEeL1qjhovso1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=